---
title: Herby Crumbed Chicken & Kumara Fries with Avocado Salad & Aioli
description: Boost the flavour of a classic chicken schnitzel by adding parsley to the golden crumb coating. Served with garlic aioli, kumara
fries and an avocado salad for a meal nobody can refuse!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-crumbed-chicken-avocado-salad-08bb17d4.jpg
